race.description: Kyneton Car & Dog Wash Mdn Plate
race.comment: CONFLICT (1) won a Pakenham jumpout before a narrow defeat there on debut. Will be presented fitter by the smart stable and maps for the run of the race. Can go one better. NATIONAL CODE (10) is also in sharp hands. Missed a nose at Sale on debut and was immediately tipped out. Resumes and has a Flemington jumpout win under the saddle. Will have come on and she's a threat. TASSORTING (7) looked good at the jumpouts and went close at Mornington on debut. He will be fitter and is also good enough to make the finish. This trio should be fighting the race out. I AM STRONG (9) resumes for a new stable and may be the best of the remainder.
